data.description: Explore this beautiful Dominic home, ready for quick move-in on a homesite boasting driveway pavers and front yard landscaping. Included features: an inviting covered entry; a teen room; a dining room in lieu of a study; a gourmet kitchen offering a butlery's pantry, a double oven, 42'' cabinets, stainless-steel appliances, quartz countertops and a center island; a roomy nook; a spacious great room; a lavish owner's suite showcasing a patio door, a private bath and a generous walk-in closet; a convenient laundry; a covered patio and a 3-car garage. This home also offers airy 10' ceilings and 8' doors, ceiling fan prewiring and additional windows in select rooms and stone tile flooring throughout. Tour today!
